    "body": "Electron doesn't have builtin APIs for serial port operations, you have to use third party modules unfortunately.\n\nWhen a module is not working perfectly, you can usually try using it in a node process and pipes the result to Electron, i.e. using node-serialport in a script with `child_process.fork`.\n"
